How much you wanna bet the Rengar had no actual plan when running around?

You may git gud, but you will ever git as gud as I was when I used Jinx's ult on Baron, simply because no enemy was visible on the minimap and not only got the Baron buff, but also a triple kill.

But since I didn't have any LoLReplay-like application on my PC at the time, it never happened, right?
I wouldve died to the red buff and then the jinx rocket wouldve flown over my body as an extra fuck you.
"Non existent *Blue Buff* "
But all he did was run in a circle
He was so close xD
Say what you will about the Rengar rework, but at least he can't use his ult to escape everything now.
